parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission shifter interlock can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The gear shifter is stuck in park
the vehicle cannot be shifted out of park
the shifter interlock lever is broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to jerk or hesitate while shifting, leading to loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission jerks or hesitates while shifting
the vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
the transmission slips or fails to engage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power train can cause the vehicle to lose power or accelerate unexpectedly, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power or accelerates unexpectedly
the transmission slips or fails to engage
the engine stalls or shuts off while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the air bag warning light can indicate a fault in the air bag system, which can lead to failure of the air bags to deploy in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The air bag warning light illuminates on the instrument panel
the horn does not sound.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupants of the vehicle are not provided with the necessary protection.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in a crash
despite the severity of the impact
resulting in injuries to the occupants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of parts to repair or replace defective airbags can leave vehicles in an unsafe condition, putting occupants at risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Receipt of recall notification
but parts are not available to repair or replace defective airbags
leaving the vehicle in an unsafe condition.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the radiator fan can cause the vehicle to overheat, leading to damage to the engine and other components, which can result in costly repairs or even engine failure.
symptoms: Loud noise
radiator fan punctured or shattered
damage to the radiator
overheating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shifter assembly can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling can cause the vehicle to lose power, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

code 1004

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cooling system can cause the vehicle to overheat, leading to damage to the engine and other components, which can result in costly repairs or even engine failure.
